OL,6,FHis death is now one of more than
OL,7,F2,000 inpatient deaths being
OL,8,Finvestigated by The Lampard Inquiry, a
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry into failings of the
OL,10,FEssex mental health care system over
OL,11,Fthe past 20 years.
OL,13,FChair Baroness Lampard began
OL,14,Foverseeing hearings into alleged
OL,15,Ffailing in September.
