OL,6,FDuring those first three weeks, the
OL,7,Finquiry heard of alleged sexual abuse
OL,8,Fon mental health units, as well as
OL,9,Fpatients, at serious risk of suicide,
OL,10,Ftaking their own lives whilst being
OL,11,Ftreated at facilities.
OL,13,FThe inquiry will begin again next
OL,14,Fweek, on November 25.
OL,16,FMargot said: "When I listen to some of
OL,17,Fthe testimonies from the Lampard
OL,18,FInquiry, it's very evident from every
OL,19,Fsingle one that a lot of the families
OL,20,Fare beside themselves with worry for
OL,21,Fthe person they love.
