OL,6,F"And you put all your faith in these
OL,7,Fexperts that are there to help and you
OL,8,Fbreathe a sigh of relief that they're
OL,9,Fin a place of safety. And it's very
OL,10,Fobvious that my dad was not in a place
OL,11,Fof safety.
OL,13,FOne of six children, Margot, who is
OL,14,Fnow 67, said her father had struggled
OL,15,Fwith his mental health for most of his
OL,16,Flife. She remembers his low moods as a
OL,17,Fchild and how he would stay in bed and
OL,18,Feat little - sometimes for up to a
OL,19,Fweek.
