OL,7,Fwould coax him out of it and their
OL,8,Fhappy family life would return to
OL,9,Fnormal.
OL,11,FTheirs was an unlikely, but enduring
OL,12,Flove story.
OL,14,FAfter being recruited into Fleming's
OL,15,Fsecret 30th Assault Unit - the
OL,16,Fintelligence unit that would inspire
OL,17,Fhis spy books - Ron took part in raids
OL,18,Fdesigned to gather information on and
OL,19,Fdestroy German specialist rockets that
OL,20,Fwere causing devastating damage to the
OL,21,FAllies.
