OL,6,FIt was following one of these
OL,7,Fmissions, in Brittany, that he met his
OL,8,Fwife, who was in the French Resistance.
OL,10,FThey knew each other for two weeks
OL,11,Fbefore he was sent to Germany. The two
OL,12,Fbegan a courtship through pen and
OL,13,Fpaper, which resulted in their wedding
OL,14,Fin 1947.
OL,16,FBut, before the boy from Dagenham
OL,17,Fcould begin his life with his wife, he
OL,18,Fwas stationed in Hong Kong guarding
OL,19,FJapanese prisoners.
