OL,4,Cof mental health services, family says
OL,6,FHe became friendly with them, some
OL,7,Fteaching him Jiu Jitsu in their cells,
OL,8,Fbefore he had to march them to the
OL,9,Fgallows.
OL,11,FIt was this experience that Margot and
OL,12,Fher family believe did the lasting
OL,13,Fdamage to his mental health, saying he
OL,14,Ffelt the deep injustice of foot
OL,15,Fsoldiers being sent to their death,
OL,16,Fwhile their commanders were only
OL,17,Fhanded house arrest.
OL,19,FShe said: "And even though I can't
OL,20,Fspeak for my dad, he would be very
OL,21,Fopen, I think, with my mum.
