OL,6,F"She was the only person he would
OL,7,Fconfide in. And so it's only really
OL,8,Fthrough my mum that I can tell you
OL,9,Fsome of how he felt in his heart. And
OL,10,Fshe would often say that she felt that
OL,11,Fthe real damage was done more post war
OL,12,Fin Hong Kong."
OL,14,FIn 1994, Ron went to a GP who
OL,15,Fprescribed him antidepressants without
OL,16,Fproper examination or counseling,
OL,17,Faccording to this family. This, they
OL,18,Fbelieve, was the catalyst for his
OL,19,Fdownward spiral.
