OL,4,Cof mental health services, family says
OL,6,F"What we noticed is he very quickly
OL,7,Fthen went into this enormous high. So
OL,8,Fhe went from being depressed to
OL,9,Fincredibly high. It was something we
OL,10,Fhad never seen," she said.
OL,12,FRon then attempted suicide, which he
OL,13,Fhad never done before, according to
OL,14,Fhis daughter. It was after this
OL,15,Fattempt when he ended up with Essex
OL,16,Fmental health services."
OL,18,FRon was then sectioned for the first
OL,19,Ftime at Runwell Hospital in Wickford.
OL,20,FBut, it wouldn't be the last.
