OL,4,Cof mental health services, family says
OL,6,FHis suffering followed an extreme
OL,7,Fpattern for the next 12 years, each
OL,8,Fmanic episode ending up with him being
OL,9,Fsectioned and then released again into
OL,10,Fthe community without any support.
OL,12,FMargot said she and her family
OL,13,Frepeatedly asked the services for
OL,14,Fhelp, but they would be "uninterested"
OL,15,Funtil he reached rock bottom and was
OL,16,Fsuicidal.
OL,18,FShe said: "I mean, they would put him
OL,19,Fon different antidepressants, they
OL,20,Fwould put him on lithium. Nothing
OL,21,Fseemed to stop this cycle.
