OL,3,CWar hero starved to death under care
OL,4,Cof mental health services, family says
OL,6,F"I felt that the treatment he was
OL,7,Fgiven put him on a track of behaviour
OL,8,Fthat would never have happened had
OL,9,Fthey not intervened with inappropriate
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,F"We didn't recognise him as the dad we
OL,13,Fknew and it's really difficult to come
OL,14,Fto terms with that."
OL,16,FRon died in May 2006 from a heart
OL,17,Fattack. He was severely malnourished
OL,18,Fand dehydrated.
