OL,6,FMargot and her family believe he would
OL,7,Fnot have died this way if he had been
OL,8,Fgiven the care he deserved.
OL,10,FAnd despite his death being nearly 20
OL,11,Fyears ago, she said their experience
OL,12,Fis still relevant to The Lampard
OL,13,FInquiry.
OL,15,F"Care and safety are the two number
OL,16,Fone things for me. I really welcome
OL,17,FThe Lampard Inquiry to look into this
OL,18,Fbecause from the testimonies I've
OL,19,Fheard, it would sound like things have
OL,20,Fgot even worse since my dad died."
